              {
                "flag": "fratBroDefeated",
                "is": false
              },
              {
                "flag": "fatChudDefeated",
                "is": false
              }
            ],
            "text": "Okay, the Bartender vouched for you. I overheard someone saying the Frat Bro at the pong table or the big dude by the taps might know the floor codes.",
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "[Exit] On it.",
                "next": "exit"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "conditions": [
              {
                "flag": "fratBroDefeated",
                "is": true
              },
              {
                "flag": "fatChudDefeated",
                "is": false
              }
            ],
            "text": "Nice job with the pong guy! But I heard you also need to talk to the big guy by the taps... Fat Chud, I think? Hurry up!",
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "[Exit] Got it.",
                "next": "exit"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "conditions": [
              {
                "flag": "fratBroDefeated",
                "is": false
              },
              {
                "flag": "fatChudDefeated",
                "is": true
              }
            ],
            "text": "Okay, you handled the big guy, but a rumor's going around that the Frat Bro at the pong table has the rest of the info. Get over there!",
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "[Exit] Got it.",
                "next": "exit"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "condition": {
              "flag": "djDefeated",
              "is": false
            },
            "text": "You got the info from both of them! Word is, the DJ controls access to the back rooms. Get to the dance floor and see what he wants.",
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "[Exit] Going.",
                "next": "exit"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "You actually got the VIP pass?! I heard the Boss is chilling in the VIP lounge... that's gotta be the way out. What are you waiting for?!",
            "options": [
              {
                "text": "[Exit] Right, sorry!",
                "next": "exit"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
